losophical writer and thinker contemporary to our time.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 10. Jan 2022) 0aAfrican AmericansxIntellectual lifey20th century. 0aPolitics and literaturezUnited StatesxHistoryy20th century. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Ethnic Studies / African American Studies.2bisacsh40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9781478022121zCo-access DOI >> click Walter de Gruyter40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781478022121423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781478022121/original  aEBA_DUK_ALL  aEBA_DUK_EALL  aEBA_DUK_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles